  "title": "Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Your responsibilities include:</strong></p><ul><li>Conceptualize M&E designs and execute the project with the detailed designs.</li><li>Manage and engage client/consultant/ contractors and local authorities to drive project execution, submission to authorities and overall on-site construction supervision.</li></ul><p><strong>What you will need:</strong></p><ul><li>A recognized university degree Mechanical or Electrical Engineering or Building Services.</li><li>Minimum 2 years’ of relevant experience in design and implementation of building services.</li><li>Strong team-working, communication and interpersonal skills. Able to build good working relationships with client and key stakeholders.</li><li>Open to opportunities to be trained on a wide range of technical and management topics.</li></ul>",
